This patch includes following fixes on ZCS 8.7.11 GA
ZCS-4115 - Bug 107925 - Persistent XSS - snippet [CWE-79]
ZCS-4116 - Bug 108265 - Persistent XSS - message view as text [CWE-79]
ZCS-4235 - Bug 108786 - Persistent XSS - content-location [CWE-79]

Please re-check your ZCS version. This patch should only be applied on 8.7.11 GA.

